data.description: Nestled in the Stonebrook subdivision of Belgrade this charming split-entry home awaits its lucky new owner. Boasting 3 beds, 2 bathrooms, a fireplace in the living room, and a fully-finished basement. Step inside, and you'll immediately feel a sense of warmth and coziness. Natural light streams through the windows, filling the rooms with a cheerful ambiance. The well-designed floor plan ensures every square foot is maximized for comfort and convenience. With a 2-car attached garage, you'll have all the storage and convenience you need for both vehicles and outdoor gear. This property is situated on a large lot, the fenced-in backyard is complete with a deck and fantastic outdoor entertaining space. Schedule your private tour, and start imagining the memories you'll create by obtaining the lifestyle you've always dreamed of – it's waiting for you here!
